<section class="bg-ivory">
  <div class="container-prose py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-[720px]">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-navy-deep text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.15] mb-8">Why Founding Faculty Matter</h2>
      <div class="rule-gold mb-10"></div>
      <div class="prose-editorial text-graphite">
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl leading-[1.75] mb-7">Institutions are not remembered simply because they were built.</p>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl leading-[1.75] mb-7">They are remembered because exceptional people chose to build them.</p>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl leading-[1.75] mb-7">Founding Faculty do more than teach.</p>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl leading-[1.75] mb-7">They help establish the academic standards, educational philosophy and culture that future educators inherit.</p>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl leading-[1.75] mb-7">For Veterinary Academy International, this is not a symbolic title.</p>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl leading-[1.75] mb-7">It is a responsibility to help shape the institution from its beginning.</p>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl leading-[1.75]">Every respected academic institution can point to the educators who shaped it in its earliest years. We hope Veterinary Academy International will be no different.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
